{"tid":921348,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"絞刑爭議下　共和黨贏密州補選","createTime":"2018-11-29T13:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T13:25:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5a17344e5d459fbee928201ae005ea76b64a0a22","tid":921348,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:18:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181129/20556914\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181129%2F20556914&d=Myni4mpKaVLfVJ%2F686klHdZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=441c2d80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181129%2F20556914&h=347e5b9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181129/20556914</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月29日 <br />\n<br />\n絞刑爭議下　共和黨贏密州補選<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181129/large/a2102a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181129%2Flarge%2Fa2102a.gif&h=9478a055&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n海德史密斯（右）慶祝勝選。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國中期選舉的最後一場選戰前日上演，密西西比州參議員補選次輪投票中，共和黨海德史密斯（Cindy Hyde-Smith）以55.2%得票率擊敗民主黨埃斯皮（Mike Espy）的44.8%，使共和黨在參議院的優勢擴大成53比47。59歲的海德史密斯成為該州首名女性當選參議員，亦使64歲的埃斯皮欲成為該州自南北戰爭後重建時期140年來首名黑人參議員的願望落空。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181129/large/a2102b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181129%2Flarge%2Fa2102b.gif&h=1af7a7b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民主黨的埃斯皮（左）落敗後擁抱妻子。<br />\n美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當選人被轟種族主義<br />\n<br />\n這場補選在本月6日因角逐的四人得票都不過半，前天進行次輪投票。埃斯皮一度以為有勝算，事關海德史密斯本月初在公開場合讚揚一名支持者時，揚言「要是他邀我觀看絞刑，我會坐在第一行」，激怒該州不少選民。因密州有38%人口是非裔，早在17世紀黑奴就被販運到該州，幾百年來一直受歧視，甚至遭種族主義者以絞刑等私刑處決。另外網傳一段影片中，海德史密斯說要「讓自由派投票困難一點」，網上亦瘋傳一張她身穿南方邦聯軍帽的相片。<br />\n<br />\n諸種言行為她惹來種族主義者和反民主的惡名。贊助她選舉的沃爾瑪百貨在爆出風波後要求退款。她其後雖道歉，但指是對手扭曲她言論。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/美聯社/法新社  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n為世界帶來歡笑不敵漸凍症《海綿寶寶》之父病逝<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n百年最強暴雨襲悉尼一死"},{"pid":"cc70fc9c1347a580e83d18414c50805e3d8a93cc","tid":921348,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:19:55.000Z","msg":"禾侵又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac76fae40614885264b64b6a46fed4a80d0bc2c","tid":921348,"uid":63184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a17344e5d459fbee928201ae005ea76b64a0a22","tid":921348,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:18:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181129/20556914\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181129%2F20556914&d=Myni4mpKaVLfVJ%2F686klHdZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=441c2d80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181129%2F20556914&h=347e5b9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181129/20556914</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月29日 <br />\n<br />\n絞刑爭議下　共和黨贏密州補選<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181129/large/a2102a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181129%2Flarge%2Fa2102a.gif&h=9478a055&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n海德史密斯（右）慶祝勝選。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國中期選舉的最後一場選戰前日上演，密西西比州參議員補選次輪投票中，共和黨海德史密斯（Cindy Hyde-Smith）以55.2%得票率擊敗民主黨埃斯皮（Mike Espy）的44.8%，使共和黨在參議院的優勢擴大成53比47。59歲的海德史密斯成為該州首名女性當選參議員，亦使64歲的埃斯皮欲成為該州自南北戰爭後重建時期140年來首名